description._content: Description: An experimental plant at M.-i-S. for treating the waste gas to produce various valuable products. A Persian research chemist at work. 1926. Date: 1926 Description: Experimental gas-cracking plant beside the gas laboratory. Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/714 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown.
